Abstract: Authorizes a rebate of state sales taxes paid by qualifying businesses on lodging
and meals for persons performing disaster or emergency-related work during a
disaster response period.
Proposed law authorizes a rebate for the actual amount of state sales tax paid by a qualifying
business on purchases of any of the following:
